headline.main: German Minister Warns UK Over Trade, Predicts Frankfurt to Gain
headline.print_headline: German Minister Warns UK Over Trade, Predicts Frankfurt to Gain

lead_paragraph: Britain would be "naive" to expect generous trade deals when it quits the European Union, the German minister responsible for its financial centre said on Monday, adding that Frankfurt would grab business from London.
